vocabinfos.mediumDef:
A man living at the time of Divided Monarchy, first mentioned at 1Ki.22.11;
father of: Zedekiah (H6667)
§ Chenaanah = "trader"
1) father of Zedekiah the false prophet of Ahab
2) son of Bilhan, grandson of Jediael, and great grandson of Benjamin and the founder of a house of Benjamin
vocabinfos._es_Definition: (a)   padre de Sedequías, falso profeta; en tiempos de Ahab; (b)   hijo de Bilhán; tribu de Benjamín
vocabinfos._zh_tw_Definition:
基拿拿 这个陽性專有名詞 人名在希伯來文的意思是 "經商者"
1) 亞哈王的假先知西底家的父親
2) 比勒罕的兒子, 耶疊的孫子, 便雅憫的曾孫 (代上 7:10)
vocabinfos._zh_Definition:
基拿拿 这个阳性专有名词 人名在希伯来文的意思是 "经商者"
1) 亚哈王的假先知西底家的父亲
2) 比勒罕的儿子, 耶迭的孙子, 便雅悯的曾孙 (代上 7:10)

vocabinfos.mediumDef:
A man of the tribe of Benjamin living at the time of Divided Monarchy, only mentioned at 1Ch.7.10;
son of: Bilhan (H1092H);
brother of: Jeush (H3266H), Benjamin (H1144H), Ehud (H0164H), Zethan (H2133), Tarshish (H8659I) and Ahishahar (H0300)
§ Chenaanah = "trader"
1) father of Zedekiah the false prophet of Ahab
2) son of Bilhan, grandson of Jediael, and great grandson of Benjamin and the founder of a house of Benjamin
